{"tid":2102143,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人開始覺得要珍惜時間，做自己想做既野","createTime":"2020-07-10T09:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T16:01:40.000Z","uid":2679,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ea84b5a0de790963ba623543e633ed8176dac4ab","tid":2102143,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"一嚟就疫情啦，二嚟見到連麵麵都有腦瘤，唔知可以人生食幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如好好地盡力一煲試下啲自己一直唔敢做既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼到左熄燈果一刻都叫唔好後悔啊，係咪先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想減肥既減肥，毒撚想表白既就表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前我旅行果陣上網識過個女仔，大家同一時間去同一個地方，每日去完啲行程講下自己去左邊到，今日遇過啲咩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但最搞笑既係，我到依家都無真正見過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依兩年幾都係周不時會傾兩句咁，傾一次可以傾成兩三個鐘，但我始終唔敢出去食下野啊，搵野玩下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家搞搞下佢都就grad，反而我到依刻都仲係好驚，真心唔想自己再係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後就覺得人可以好快就死，可能下一秒就暈左，希望自己有翻啲勇氣，唔好再有遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2F0m58YIMPs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2F0m58YIMPs&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwummt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=983d0c8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2F0m58YIMPs</a><br />\n每個平凡的自我 都曾幻想過 <br />\n以你為名的小說 會是枯燥 或是雋永<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea1e89fd39372fefb10cbd783cadc5ec5e62488","tid":2102143,"uid":2679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:12:20.000Z","msg":"珍惜光陰，唔好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8749349d43ff8a19aab075199aa75ccb5be4260","tid":2102143,"uid":258784,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T0